-- Portugal Telecom Freezes Wages Until 2013, Dinheiro Vivo Reports
-- B y   H e n r i q u e   A l m e i d a
-- 2012-09-14T14:59:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-14/portugal-telecom-freezes-wages-until-2013-dinheiro-vivo-reports.html
Portugal Telecom SGPS SA (PTC)  will
freeze workers’ salaries this year and in 2013, business news
website Dinheiro Vivo  reported  today, citing a statement from
the company’s workers commission.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Henrique Almeida in Lisbon at 
 halmeida5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
